  "keyFeatures": [
    "Real-time inflation calculator with historical data from ArgentinaDatos API",
    "Dollar exchange rate display for multiple currency types (oficial, blue, bolsa, cripto, tarjeta, etc.)",
    "Interactive historical dollar price chart with adjustable time ranges (1 week to all-time)",
    "ARS/USD currency converter with live exchange rates from DolarAPI",
    "Collapsible inflation index table organized by decade and year",
    "Interactive inflation trend chart with Chart.js",
    "Deployed on Vercel with SSR via Astro adapter"
